k config set-context $(kubectl config current-context) --namespace=dev    //get into namespace dev, afterwards all the performancd would be done in this namespace

k get pods --all-namespace    
or
k get pods -A

1. Create a POD in the finance namespace.
Use the spec given below:
Name: redis
Image name: redis

A:
kubectl run redis --image=redis -n finance
or
k config set-context $(kubectl config current-context) --namespace=finance
kubectl run redis --image=redis

